OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mixed day of
OL,6,Fshowers with some bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Showers will be heavy and
OL,8,Fperhaps thundery at times. Fresh
OL,9,Fwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FHeavy and perhaps thundery
OL,12,Fshowers continuing through the evening
OL,13,Fwith some clear spells. Showers easing
OL,14,Fovernight with clear spells, but low
OL,15,Fcloud and rain spreading into the
OL,16,Fsouth around dawn.
OL,17,
OL,18,CThursday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks
OL,19,Fof rain spreading north to all parts
OL,20,Fthrough the day. Breezy around western
OL,21,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
